This topic describes how to use Reliability View for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).

##<a id='grafana'></a>Accessing Grafana

The Reliability View for PCF includes [Grafana](https://grafana.com/), a platform for exploring and visualizing metrics. To access it, navigate to the route you previously set up for Grafana in <a href="installing.html">the installation guide</a>.  The username and password are located in the `Credentials` tab of the Reliability View for PCF tile with the name `Grafana Login`.
